						               													<description>Screwed . . . the card game where you're in it for yourself!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are no partners!!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The object of the game is to obtain the highest score by accurately predicting how many tricks you will take each round. The more you frustrate your opponents by taking their tricks or making them take tricks they do not want, the better your chances of winning will be.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round the strategy changes and you can try to bribe, beg, or sweet talk your opponents into helping you make your bid. If you fail, you can get revenge in the next round. Revenge is sweet! Players will find themselves with impetuous feelings of laughter, joy, hat, annoyance, excitement, or antagonism.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The trick to winning this challenging game is a mixture of skill and a lot of luck. No matter what your skill level, everyone has a chance to win this stimulating game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Good luck . . . you'll need it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the back of the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contains six plastic screws with nuts used for bidding.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
